    "PHASE: Starter | Revenue: $0–2K/mo | Clients: 4 | Followers: 110",
    "GOAL: Build a gym (long-term) — online coaching = capital vehicle",
    "",
    "FLAG: Goal alignment is the first conversation. Shannon wants a gym, not an online business. The reframe: online coaching IS the gym road. $15K/mo x 24 months at 30% savings = $108K gym down payment.",
    "",
    "NAMED MECHANISM (Recommended):",
    "The BYLT Performance Protocol — 12-week 1:1 coaching: customized strength + conditioning + weekly check-ins",
