    "- 'You used to be an athlete but don't feel like that guy anymore' — identity hook",
    "- 'If you're a dad who used to be in shape but can't find time' — dad avatar hook",
    "These hooks are genuinely good. They just need to be in reel format and connected to an offer.",
    "",
    "ENTITY GAP: 0 paid ads | ~15–20 posts (static only) | 0 named mechanisms | 0 purchase path",
    "",
    "TOP 6 HOOKS:",
    "1. 'You used to be an athlete. You were that guy. Comment BUILT when eventually becomes now.' [Identity reel — CTA: Comment BUILT]",
    "2. 'For dads who used to be in shape and can't find time — I built this for you. 4 hours a week.' [Dad reel]",
    "3. 'The BYLT Performance Protocol: compound strength, conditioning that doesn't destroy you, accountability that holds.' [Mechanism reveal]",
    "4. 'Most men's programs are built for 22-year-olds with 2 hours a day. Here is what actually works with real life.' [Villain frame]",
    "5. 'Every Sunday we train together. Here is what 8 weeks looks like.' [Community proof reel]",
    "6. 'My wife and I coach together. Here is what we built for men who want to be strong for their family.' [Couple differentiation]",
    "",
    "CONSTRAINT STACK:",
    "P1: No defined online offer — no purchase path exists. Fix: The BYLT Performance Protocol at $1,500 on a Carrd.co page this week.",
    "P1: Online coaching not framed as gym capital vehicle — reframe first, then tactics.",
    "P2: 110 followers + static-only content = no organic reach. Fix: Upgrade 2 best hooks to reels, post 3x/week.",
    "P3: No DM funnel or booking system — set up ManyChat + Calendly at Week 3.",
    "OK: Avatar empathy is real — the hooks Shannon writes naturally are genuinely good.",
    "",
    "90-DAY PRIORITY ORDER:",
    "1. Goal alignment conversation — online coaching = gym capital (Day 1)",
    "2. Name and launch The BYLT Performance Protocol at $1,500 (Days 1–5)",
    "3. Film identity reel: 'You used to be that guy' (Days 3–10)",
    "4. DM 20 warm contacts in the avatar — personal launch (Days 5–14)",
    "5. Install ManyChat + post 3x/week from hook bank (Days 10–90)",
    "6. Film husband & wife differentiation reel (Days 21–45)"
  ].join("\n");
  navigator.clipboard.writeText(text).then(function() {
    var el = document.getElementById("copy-confirm");
    el.style.opacity = "1";
    setTimeout(function(){ el.style.opacity = "0"; }, 2500);
  });
}
window.addEventListener("scroll", function() {
  var scrollY = window.scrollY + 80;
  ["wins","phase","intel","constraints","plan"].forEach(function(id) {
    var el = document.getElementById(id);
    if (!el) return;
    if (el.offsetTop <= scrollY && el.offsetTop + el.offsetHeight > scrollY) {
      document.querySelectorAll(".nav-link").forEach(function(a){ a.classList.remove("active"); });
      var active = document.querySelector('.nav-link[href="#' + id + '"]');
      if (active) active.classList.add("active");
    }
  });
});
</script>
